{
  "texts": [
    "For the hybrid deep learning model CNN-LSTM can increase the performance of BERT but not significantly with accuracy, precision, and recall by 0.0085.",
    "The order of the performance evaluation results of the BERT-based deep learning model is CNN, LSTM-CNN, LSTM, and CNN-LSTM.",
    "Meanwhile, BERT-NN shows the lowest performance.",
    "The evaluation performance of the BERT-based deep learning model was carried out for analyzing the sentiments of social media users regarding the 2024 presidential election.",
    "The text representation method uses BERT with CNN, LSTM, CNN-LSTM, and LSTM-CNN models."
  ]
}